snippet.title: Guns of Boom - New Trailer - "Rewind"
snippet.description:
Introducing our brand new "Rewind" cinematic trailer! Guns of Boom is a team-based PvP action with super easy controls. Get ready for battle! #GodsofBoom

Play now: http://gigam.es/GoB
Join our Discord: http://discord.gg/godsofboom
Visit our website: http://godsofboom.com
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/godsofboom/ 
Talk to us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/godsofboom
